nodes.text: The Gubbur was a frog like creature native to Corellia. It had a long boney ridge coming from its nose and two antennae coming out of its mouth. Gubburs had three long whiskers, useful for sensing tectonic motion and could possibly predict earthquakes. It could also be found on Endor.
Gubburs appeared in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
